data.description: Starter home alert or down sizing! Close to shopping centers and schools. Don't let the square footage fool you.  This home has an enclosed carport with a/c unit, that can be turned back if desired.  This home also has a family room that is currently used as a bedroom with an a/c unit. Home has new roof 2017, new 3 ton A/C February of 2023, and new updated electric panel.  Home has a nice size back yard for all your familly gatherings.  This home is fenced and has fruit trees (mango, banana, lemon tree, cactus, and Moringa tree)! 18 inch Tile throught out the home. Put this on your list to see!
